---
import DetailLayout from '../layouts/DetailLayout.astro';
---
<DetailLayout title="Sketchware for Android">
  <section class="site-section" id="section-project-info">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row mb-5 align-items-center">
          <div class="col-md-6 pr-lg-5 mb-5 mb-lg-0">
            <div class="device-wrapper">
              <div class="device" data-device="Pixel" data-orientation="portrait" data-color="black">
                <div class="screen">
                  <img src="/images/sketch_android_main.gif" class="sketch-main-img">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="section-heading">
              <h2>Sketchware for <strong>Android</strong></h2>
            </div>
            <p><span class="date"><span class="icon-calendar"></span> October 2017 - August 2019 </span></p>
            <p class="lead">블록형 프로그래밍 언어를 기반으로 안드로이드 앱을 제작하는 앱</p>
            <p class="mb-5">글로벌 100만 다운로드 앱의 Google Play Console 퍼블리시 자동화 구현
              <br>Firebase Storage · Bluetooth · OkHttp3 등 블럭 프로그래밍 라이브러리 기획 및 개발
              <br>레이아웃/로직 공유 플랫폼 및 글로벌 다국어 strings.xml 공유 플랫폼 개발
              <br>서버 기반 WaterFall 방식 광고 미디에이션 로직 구현
            </p>
              <!-- <a href="#section-contact" class="btn btn-primary px-4 py-2 btn-sm smoothscroll">Go To Market</a> -->
            <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.besome.sketch">
              <img src="/images/icons/google_play_badge.png" class="img-fluid google-play-badge">
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="site-section bg-light " id="section-works">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-12 mb-5">
            <div class="section-heading text-center">
              <h2>My <strong>Works</strong></h2>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal1">
              <h3>Google Play Console 퍼블리시 자동화 구현</h3>
              <span class="school">#full_stack #google_publisher_api #google_o_auth</span>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal2">
              <h3>블럭 프로그래밍 라이브러리 기획 및 개발</h3>
              <span class="school">#firebase_storage #bluetooth #okhttp3 #location_manager #gradle</span>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal3">
              <h3>레이아웃 · 로직 공유 플랫폼 개발</h3>
              <span class="school">#full_stack #java #spring_framework #my_sql #my_batis</span>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal4">
              <h3>글로벌 다국어 strings.xml 공유 플랫폼 개발</h3>
              <span class="school">#full_stack #aes256 #xml_parse</span>
            </div>
            <div class="resume-item mb-4" data-toggle="modal" href="#portfolioModal5">
              <h3>광고 미디에이션 로직 구현</h3>
              <span class="school">#facebook_audience_network #google_admob #ad_mediation</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="portfolio-modal modal fade" id="portfolioModal1" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
